or life. Section 62 of the same Act deals with associated offences, such as attempts and assaults for the purpose of committing buggery, and specifically covers indecent assaults on a male person; a maximum penalty of two years\rquote 
 imprisonment is provided. Section 11 of the Act of 1885 provides as follows:- 
